      <title>随着犯罪转向网络空间，日本将不再设立全天候警务哨所</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/japan-to-shift-away-from-24-7-police-outposts-as-crime-moves-to-cyberspace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人口减少和网络犯罪增加，日本正在考虑更好地利用执法资源，从而改变在社区哨所全天候派驻警察的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/japan-to-shift-away-from-24-7-police-outposts-as-crime-moves-to-cyberspace</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 08:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
